InterContinental Mark Hopkins;
Dog friendly-not, people friendly with dogs-definitely not! Nob Hill address; how pretentious the address is California St. and Mason.
The front desk staff was snobbish from check in to check out-Really? I have dogs and you are a dog friendly hotel- so get over yourself and make an effort to make your human and dog guests feel welcome! Considering that we are paying top dollar to stay at your hotel loose the attitude and treat every guest with the same courteousness and respect that you otherwise server to all your guests w/out pets!
